@RPG_WEAPON_MENU(L_I)
#DIM L_I
#DIM L_INPUT
CLEARLINE LINECOUNT
DRAWLINE
CALL C_PICTURE_RD(L_I)
DRAWLINE
PRINTFORML 【経験値:{CFlag:L_I:住人_経験値}】【資金:{MONEY}】
DRAWLINE
PRINTFORML [0] 武装強化(経験値・資金消費)
